  "title": "Production Planner (Aerospace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop production plans and schedules that meet customer orders while minimizing inventory.</li><li> Oversee inventory levels and supply chain logistics to prevent shortages or excess stock.</li><li>Work with production teams to ensure smooth and efficient operations, adjusting schedules as needed.</li><li>Use production and sales data to forecast demand, identify inefficiencies, and make improvements.</li><li>Communicate with sales, logistics, and customer service to handle order changes or delays.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Mechanical / Precision Engineering or relevant</li><li>Min 2 years of experience in Production Planning in Aerospace Industry</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
